<br>
Good day to all reading these inked lines. I am Eumdiine, a beguiler currently of the 55th season. I have enjoyed great freedom in my travels. This chosen path has also made me a bit eccentric. I do love to entertain others with stories and animated objects dancing in unison. I find myself desiring a social atmosphere more and more these days.<br>
<br>
 I am in search of home but not any home. I seek companions of a true and trustworthy nature. I have been unsuccessful in my search to date. Instead of finding a home, I have found gatherings of individuals that must have not been held enough during childhood as they continually tried to grope me. I have also discovered incoherent babblers of nonsensical topics such as a play station, whatever that be. Such gatherings I am not interested in joining, instead I seek those come together as equals and choose to follow the hierarchy of such a gathering. I would hope these individuals would speak of nonsensical topics in certain areas, perhaps a banter room, instead of everywhere.<br>
<br>
I also seek an active guild estate area. I do enjoy visiting the tavern after a hunt and chatting with those around me. I have, however, noticed a slight problem with this. There area those that feel the need to recite my actions for me in such area. I am my own individual and can must assuredly think and act myself. <br>
<br>
Please contact me if there is some desire to meet me. I would like to wander into your halls and meet you if you think I would make a positive contribution to your guild.<br>
<br>
Sincerely, <br>
Eum<br>
<br>
(OOC: Looking for a role playing guild. I am also looking for the type of role playing on the message boards that permits each individual to only govern the conversation and actions of his/her character. To illustrate: if you toss a ball at someone’s head, it is up to that person to decide whether it hits him/her or not and to respond appropriately with the reaction.)<br>
